{
  "id": "68fdf7d5b157b74a90363047",
  "title": "140字改行おじさん",
  "created": 1761474519,
  "updated": 1761752346,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "68fdf7d5b157b74a90363047",
      "text": "140字改行おじさん",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1761474519,
      "updated": 1761474520
    },
    {
      "id": "68fdf7d800000000000e0e8a",
      "text": "[/arpla/140字改行おじさん]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1761474520,
      "updated": 1761474521
    },
    {
      "id": "68fdf8a40000000000adf180",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1761474724,
      "updated": 1761474724
    },
    {
      "id": "68feed2b0000000000479567",
      "text": "なんで140字なのか根拠が知りたい[suto3.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1761537323,
      "updated": 1761537370
    },
    {
      "id": "68feed2b0000000000479568",
      "text": "　原稿用紙準拠なら、200字",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1761537323,
      "updated": 1761537418
    },
    {
      "id": "68feedf4000000000047956a",
      "text": "　X/[Twitter]準拠？まさかね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1761537524,
      "updated": 1761565408
    },
    {
      "id": "68feed4d0000000000479569",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1761537358,
      "updated": 1761537358
    },
    {
      "id": "68fdf7d900000000000e0e8b",
      "text": "[- 80字] 78字改行おじさん",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1761474521,
      "updated": 1761537657
    },
    {
      "id": "68fdfd430000000000adf183",
      "text": "　[パソコン通信]時代の風習",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1761475907,
      "updated": 1761475951
    },
    {
      "id": "68fdf8910000000000adf17f",
      "text": " IBMの端末装置が80字x25行だった時代の名残",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1761474706,
      "updated": 1761475755
    },
    {
      "id": "68fdfcab0000000000adf182",
      "text": " 日本語は全角文字（半角文字2つ分）なので、39字改行になる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1761475756,
      "updated": 1761537837
    },
    {
      "id": "68feee7b000000000047956b",
      "text": " 今調べたら、78字だった。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1761537659,
      "updated": 1761537694
    },
    {
      "id": "68feee9f000000000047956c",
      "text": " 　78文字 + CR + LF で80字になる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1761537695,
      "updated": 1761537738
    },
    {
      "id": "68ff0b8a00000000006a15e5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1761545097,
      "updated": 1761545097
    },
    {
      "id": "68ff0b8a00000000006a15e6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1761545097,
      "updated": 1761545097
    },
    {
      "id": "68ff0ac600000000006a15e2",
      "text": "80x25 がターミナルの一つの基準的にあったのだけど、IBMの端末由来だったのか[taktamur.icon]",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1761544901,
      "updated": 1761545113
    },
    {
      "id": "68ff0b2900000000006a15e4",
      "text": "  [IBM PC]",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1761545000,
      "updated": 1761545008
    },
    {
      "id": "68ff0aee00000000006a15e3",
      "text": " さらに昔のIBMの[パンチカード]が80x25の由来 [suto3.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1761544941,
      "updated": 1761565530
    },
    {
      "id": "68ff5b770000000000127fc9",
      "text": "  データ入力とかで、パンチカードと同じ80x25が都合がよかったため端末もそうなった",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1761565559,
      "updated": 1761565693
    },
    {
      "id": "6900c0c30000000000cae81b",
      "text": "   おお、なるほど[taktamur.icon]",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1761657027,
      "updated": 1761657034
    },
    {
      "id": "68ff5b160000000000127fc8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1761565462,
      "updated": 1761565462
    },
    {
      "id": "68ff22f20000000000dc5abc",
      "text": "140は[久住哲.icon]さんによるマスキングだと想像[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1761551091,
      "updated": 1761551158
    },
    {
      "id": "68ff23130000000000dc5abf",
      "text": "\t実際はたぶん「画面内で折り返しをつくらないマン」だったのではないか",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1761551124,
      "updated": 1761551140
    },
    {
      "id": "68ff23760000000000dc5aca",
      "text": "\t\t[https://gyazo.com/6c178c9191867d40c2e45ca9c18f4ac8]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1761551224,
      "updated": 1761551246
    },
    {
      "id": "68ff23770000000000dc5acb",
      "text": "\t\tこんな感じで？",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1761551224,
      "updated": 1761551228
    },
    {
      "id": "68ff22f20000000000dc5abd",
      "text": "\t折り返さないマンはメール文化でもよく見る",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1761551091,
      "updated": 1761551253
    },
    {
      "id": "68ff23230000000000dc5ac0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1761551140,
      "updated": 1761551140
    },
    {
      "id": "6902342d0000000000eea7d8",
      "text": "逆に電子媒体の文章で句点で改行しない理由がわからない。[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1761752110,
      "updated": 1761752145
    },
    {
      "id": "690234530000000000eea7da",
      "text": "\t紙面で文末でも改行せずに文を続けて敷き詰めるのは、紙がもったいないからだ。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1761752147,
      "updated": 1761752251
    },
    {
      "id": "690234760000000000eea7db",
      "text": "\t潤沢にスクロールできる電子媒体なら全ての文末を改行したほうが文章構造がわかり易かろう。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1761752183,
      "updated": 1761752228
    },
    {
      "id": "690234e50000000000eea7dc",
      "text": "\tなんなら句点どころかたまに読点ですら改行するのに。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1761752294,
      "updated": 1761752346
    },
    {
      "id": "6902342d0000000000eea7d9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1761752110,
      "updated": 1761752110
    },
    {
      "id": "68fdf7df00000000000e0e8d",
      "text": "cf. [井戸端における暗黙のルールみたいなもの]",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1761474528,
